Sentencas: A planar solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) was fabricated using a commercial Nilyttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) anode support, an YSZ/gadolinium-doped ceria (GDC) thin-film electrolyte, and a composite cathode of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (LSCF/GDC).
Titulo: Fabrication and Performance Investigation of Three-Cell SOFC Stack Based on Anode-Supported Cells With Magnetron Sputtered Electrolyte

Sentencas: A small, three-cell, SOFC stack is assembled using 10 cm x 10cm single cells, metallic interconnects, and glass-based sealing.
Titulo: Fabrication and Performance Investigation of Three-Cell SOFC Stack Based on Anode-Supported Cells With Magnetron Sputtered Electrolyte

Sentencas: The stack performance was examined at various fuel flow rates of H-2+N-2 and air at a fixed temperature of 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and Performance Investigation of Three-Cell SOFC Stack Based on Anode-Supported Cells With Magnetron Sputtered Electrolyte

Sentencas: The three-cell stack with a crossflow design produced peak power density of 0.216 W/cm(2 )or about 39 W total power at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and Performance Investigation of Three-Cell SOFC Stack Based on Anode-Supported Cells With Magnetron Sputtered Electrolyte
